eite de oliva.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"TrT0Xe\">Sal.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"TrT0Xe\">laurel.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"TrT0Xe\">Orégano, pimienta</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--preparacón-->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col s12\">\r\n<div class=\"card\">\r\n<div class=\"card-content\">\r\n<div class=\"card deep-purple darken-4\">\r\n<div class=\"card-content\">\r\n<h4 class=\"white-text\"><i class=\"material-icons left\">done_all</i>Listado de recetas por categoría platos</h4>\r\n<ol class=\"numbered-list ui-sortable\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; counter-reset: numList 0; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; padding: 0px 0px 1px; color: #484432; font-family: Lato, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" data-behavior=\"sortable\" data-sort-url=\"/co/recipes/93728-espaguetis-al-ajillo/steps/sort\" data-record-list=\"  &lt;li class=&quot;step numbered-list__item card-sm&quot; id=&quot;new_step&quot; data-record=&quot;/co/recipes/93728-espaguetis-al-ajillo/steps&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;div data-field-group&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;numbered-list__contents&quot;&gt;\r\n        &lt;div class=&quot;step__description&quot;&gt;\r\n          &lt;div class=&quot;prose&quot;&gt;\r\n            &lt;div itemprop=&quot;recipeInstructions&quot; data-field=&quot;textarea&quot; data-field-name=&quot;description&quot; data-field-hint=\'Hacer clic en Intro para añadir otro paso\' data-placeholder=&quot;Describe cómo lo hiciste...&quot; data-maxlength=&quot;500&quot;&gt;\r\n              &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n            &lt