aso\" data-placeholder=\"Describe cómo lo hiciste...\" data-maxlength=\"500\">\r\n<ol class=\"numbered-list ui-sortable\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; counter-reset: numList 0; list-style: none; padding: 0px 0px 1px; color: #484432; font-family: Lato, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" data-behavior=\"sortable\" data-sort-url=\"/es/recipes/98202-camarones-al-ajillo/steps/sort\" data-record-list=\" &lt;li class=&quot;step numbered-list__item card-sm&quot; id=&quot;new_step&quot; data-record=&quot;/es/recipes/98202-camarones-al-ajillo/steps&quot;&gt; &lt;div data-field-group&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;numbered-list__contents&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;step__description&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;prose&quot;&gt; &lt;div itemprop=&quot;recipeInstructions&quot; data-field=&quot;textarea&quot; data-field-name=&quot;description&quot; data-field-hint=\'Hacer clic en Intro para añadir otro paso\' data-placeholder=&quot;Describe cómo lo hiciste...&quot; data-maxlength=&quot;500&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;step-image&quot; data-field=&quot;image&quot; data-field-name=&quot;images[1]&quot; data-ajax-upload=&quot;/es/step/images&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;step-image__container image&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;image-upload editor__tool&quot;&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;img-responsive droppable__placeholder&quot; src=&quot;//global.cpcdn.com/en/assets/blank_step-f3715c473b85d0fc6a78e9802b08024eaf50d5893e8cdbb1b9bdfccc6c6f9186.jpg&quot; /&gt; &lt;input type=&quot;file&quot; name=&quot;file&quot; aria-label=&q